window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>NOW A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES!</b></p> <p><b>The bestselling author and creator of the hit Netflix drama </b><b><i>The Stranger </i></b><b>takes listeners into the heart of family loyalty in this twisty thriller that proves that the darkest secrets are often closest to home.</b></p> <p>Paul Copeland, a New Jersey county prosecutor, is still grieving the loss of his sister twenty years ago - the night she walked into the woods, never to be seen again. But now, a homicide victim is found with evidence linking him to the disappearance. The victim could be the boy who vanished along with Paul's sister. And, as hope rises that his sister could still be alive, dangerous secrets from his family's past threaten to tear apart everything Paul has been trying to hold together....</p>"; 
